commit.message:
Merge pull request #10 from dabrahams/volatile/elscreen

Nicer-looking elscreen tabs

Now that we have the button box on the active tab, the text on
inactive tabs can be a bit brighter.

Tried zenburn-blue-2 but it goes a bit too far, IMO.
Further improve the appearance of active elscreen tabs

Merge pull request #9 from dabrahams/volatile/widgets

Better face for inactive widgets

Merge pull request #5 from dabrahams/volatile/cite-bg

Slightly highlight background of cited text

Slightly highlight background of cited text

Provides useful visual separation when you read messages from people
who don't separate cited text from their reply by a blank line.
Do not set `erc-mode-line-format' (dubious for a color theme).
Move Gnus, ERC and `term' junk to the bottom of the file.
Change org-mode code to look like the rest of the file.
Remove old comments that have become irrelevant.
Add workaround for M-x term problem.

Add org-mode faces from Adrian C. and Bastien Guerry.

Remove `color-theme.el' as upstream has finally put all those other color themes in a separate file.  The color theme library is available in Debian as `emacs-color-themes'.
